data.description: Welcome home to this spacious and very well-maintained home featuring 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, fully loaded eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, living room and family room with wood-burning fireplace and beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. Also featuring a generous sized Owners Suite with lots of closet space and an updated on-suite. You and the family will enjoy a spacious fenced-in back yard in a park like setting with a deck and a one car garage. Recent improvements include newer roof, electrical panel, stove, refrigerator, microwave, washer, dryer, and hot water tank. Master bathroom updated. Newer master bedroom windows, and master bathroom roof vent was installed. Newer carpet in master bedroom and family room. The home has glass block windows and a nice sized basement waiting for your finishing touches. Selling As-Is. Buyer to accept Point of Sale Violations. Owner not making any additional improvements or repairs. Don't delay. Set your appointment Today!
